### IMPORTANT - NAME CHANGE
This package has been renamed to **fenix-web-server-pre** to comply with Chocolatey's Package ID naming conventions.
Installing this version will automatically install the new package as a dependency.
You may safely uninstall this package (fenix-web-server-beta) after the migration.
